---
title: Beef Tenderloin and Sun-Dried Tomato Cream Sauce with Walnut-Topped Asparagus
description: Break out the fine china for this feast! Beef tenderloin is topped with creamy, umami-rich sun-dried tomato cream sauce. Asparagus tossed in Parmesan and finished with toasted walnuts rounds out this luxe meal.
